he public API path still exercises:\n  - `KeyPair.load(...)`\n  - `KeyPair.setPassphrase(...)`\n  - `KeyPair.writePrivateKey(...)`\n  - `KeyPair.decrypt(...)`\n  - `KeyPair.getFingerPrint()`\n\nThis should allow the `KeyPair.genCipher`, `KeyPair.genHash`, and `KeyPair.genRandom` `Class.forName(...)` / `newInstance()` call sites to execute successfully instead of failing with `ClassNotFoundException`/`NullPointerException` under Native Image.\n\nI did not run tests locally, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b7c0e5b4bf7f843016a11077db4ac8196b3a9863bc09fc759\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 477, "output": 1288, "cacheRead": 51712, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 53477, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1779500909157, "responseId": "resp_0b7c0e5b4bf7f843016a11076dba6c819686c6d7bc265dd29b"}}
